JOHANNESBURG – The new presenter for Mzansi Magic's hit reality show Our Perfect Wedding, Kayise Ngqula, raised the ire of fans on Sunday night. Kayise Ngqula named as new #OPWPresenterSearch host The show follows the journey couples take as they head for the altar. On Sunday, Ngqula angered viewers when she broke the confidence of the bride and asked the groom a question the bride expressly said she did not want to talk about. Fans took to Twitter, saying Ngqula had disrespected the bride. Fans of the show also appear to think Kayise is too loud. eNCA